node.text:
4,843 ACRES of RAINFOREST SAVED @moetchandon x @ambush_official collaboration donation made it possible. 🙏🏽💚🍃
 
As you remember, #moëtchandon pledged to donate a portion of profits from the sale of limited-edition Moët & Chandon x #AMBUSH bottles to the @worldlandtrust – an international conservation charity that protects threatened natural habitats – to help preserve the #Canandé Reserve in the Ecuadorian #Chocó Forest, a place as biodiverse as the Amazon rainforest but far more threatened. The remarkable donation has had a direct impact on stopping the deforestation of the Chocó, not just for the sake of its fragile species but also to combat one of the causes of climate change.
 
I want to take this moment to thank you Moët & Chandon, for making my idea come to life and for everyone who purchased the bottles. You guys' support has contributed to the impact of this noble amazing cause! 

Here's the video from the @WorldLandTrust bout this donation: 

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SfrGhur_rzc

node.text:
Fashion and sport can collide in non-traditional and compelling ways, demonstrating how athletic wear can be transformed through culture. Inspired by Japan's motorcycle subculture, I designed the Motorcycle Jacket and Pant to be as futuristically fashionable as they are functional. The collection's bright pink and neon green colors nod to Tokyo's bright lights and anime culture, illustrating the surprising ways sport can transform the aesthetics of daily life. And thank you @theestallion for gettin on this ride with us.

UNISEX @AMBUSH_official x @NIKE FA2021 COLLECTION taking off on 7.30.2021 JAPAN + WORLDWIDE

node.text:
6AM 🕕

A 24-hour house party on the shores of a lake, a long-awaited escape from the city, and the promise of a celebration for the @ambush_official AW2021 campaign ☁️🌥⛅️🌤☀️🌞

The AW2021 COLLECTION is launching today worldwide and later for Japan 🌞

Creative direction: @wesayhi @ambush_official
Styling: Carlos Nazario @mr_carlos_nazario
Photo: Harley Weir @harleyweir
Casting: Rachel Chandler @midlandagency
Hair: Louis Ghewy @louisghewy + Gabriele Marozzi @gab_marozzi
Makeup: Masae Ito @masae__ito + Mio Iguchi @mioiguchi
Production: @collateralfilms_official
Set Design: @lorenzolazzari73

#ambush #trippy #anotherworld #morningroutine #newcollection2021
